        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4426447266" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9848604029520415573">While the writing was very poetic and lyrical, the overall story was disengaging. I was not a fan of the switching between first and third person point of views, nor was I a fan of the way the story was structured. The jumps between past and present were often sudden and abrupt, leaving me awfully confused.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


